SPARQL Generate over Apache Jena 0.10-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena
Configuration classes for SPARQL-Generate over Jena.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.engine
Classes to create and execute generation plans.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.engine.impl
Implementations of classes to execute generation plans.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.function.library
Contains the SPARQL custom functions for extracting strings from common data formats, defined by the SPARQL Generate specification.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.iterator
Contains the model for SPARQL Generate iterator functions.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.iterator.library
Contains the SPARQL Generate iterator functions from common data formats, defined by the SPARQL Generate specification.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.lang
Contains the Parser classes for SPARQL Generate queries, that actually extend the SPARQL 1.1 query syntax.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.query
Contains the model for SPARQL Generate queries.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.serializer
Contains the classes to serialize SPARQL Generate queries.
com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.syntax
Contains the models of elements of SPARQL Generate queries.
